						<%= image_tag "beerance_internal_iphone.png", class: 'hiw_iphone'%>
					</div>
					<div class="large-7 columns">
						<h2>Simple & Easy</h2>
						<ol>
							<li><span>Launch the app.</span></li>
							<li><span>Get your current location by the geo locator or Enter a Zip code.</span></li>
							<li><span>Press 'Get Specials'.</span></li>
							<li><span>Beerance lists price, beer name & style, bar name, serving size and sistance.</span></li>
							<li><span>Click arrow button for more information on the bar including map directions, hours, phone and web site information.</span></li>
						</ol>
						<!--
						<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/beerance/id715736707?mt=8&uo=4" target="itunes_store" class="appstore"></a>
						-->
						<%= link_to "", new_registration_path(resource_name), class: 'bartry' %>						
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="large-12 columns">
						<p>Beerance works like this – consumers download the Free app, enter your location and Beerance Specials quickly appear on a map in relation to your current location or by entering a ZIP code. Choose a proximity of 5, 10 or 25 mile radius. Have a  few favorite pubs? Just favorite them and they will always appear at the the top of the list. Beerance gives you the ability to Share Beerance Specials with your friends via Facebook, Twitter or Text.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="highlightbackground" style="margin-bottom:23px;">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="large-12 columns asd">
						<%= image_tag "beerance_baricon.png"%><h2 style="margin-bottom:0;">For the Bar Owner</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="large-6 columns">
						<ul>
							<li>Move inventory quickly.</li>
							<li>Connect with the mobile generation.</li>
							<li>Announce Beerance specials nightly.</li>
							<li>Easy to use tools.</li>
							<li>Multiple payment plan options.</li>
							<li>Create loyalty and keep in front of your regulars and attract new customers.</li>
							<li>Easy account setup.</li>
							<li>Choose a plan, first month is FREE.</li>
							<li>Add multiple bars or locations.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="large-6 columns">
						<ul>
							<li>Easily add specials by entering beer name, style & price</li>
							<li>All specials are archived so you can easily reactivate any special at a future time</li>
							<li>Add specials from your mobile device or desktop computers</li>
							<li>Specials auto expire after the following day, avoiding you the hassle of manually ending the special</li>
							<li>Beerance sends an alert prior to the special expiring giving you the opportunity to extend the special, or, do nothing and it will automatically close and be archived</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="large-12 columns asd">
						<p>Beerance has a simple account setup process. Once you create your account, choose your plan, you are ready to start your first special. The easy to use administration area allows you to quickly add multiple Specials. Beerance specials automatically expire the following day they were created. Want to run the special longer? Beerance sends an automated reminder asking you if you'd like to extend the special. One touch extends it for another day. Ignore the alert and The special automatically expires but stays archived. Get Started!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				</div>
